drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBMQ040EGAUiEwib58S9t-uTAxWdSfIAHbxxCxhIg9zP6Y2bgYrvAcoBBPZywNQ=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbWlacGNTZ01iWU96eEZ2Y0JtX2VPeTVmcHlZUXxBQ3Jtc0ttdkZodzdCOVpaelVGRnd2SnRFME9FUXNoT2JoZUtidFdMdWczNi1TWXRKN29raDJ2QWpCNWw5Um9NNHFzZXRBMVAzc0pZVFF1OHU2MVNzVW9heVhQQ2l0NnpEWG9WVHlGRVFLN2hNZHFEMzlMdV9rUQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=7xQE2N0z7gM","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbWlacGNTZ01iWU96eEZ2Y0JtX2VPeTVmcHlZUXxBQ3Jtc0ttdkZodzdCOVpaelVGRnd2SnRFME9FUXNoT2JoZUtidFdMdWczNi1TWXRKN29raDJ2QWpCNWw5Um9NNHFzZXRBMVAzc0pZVFF1OHU2MVNzVW9heVhQQ2l0NnpEWG9WVHlGRVFLN2hNZHFEMzlMdV9rUQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=7xQE2N0z7gM","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBMQ040EGAUiEwib58S9t-uTAxWdSfIAHbxxCxhIg9zP6Y2bgYrvAcoBBPZywNQ=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbGRXRGIxekJCc05uZ3lCR2tIVzRfSU9QZE15QXxBQ3Jtc0tsY0pzYWI2aUNiUl9kWjJLZ3FLb1gzRnotR2RyVnZFOTRCLU16cU5jOTBBdWxibEpUMWN5WDBJenNkRHdGS1hkdDdncHBISTRIalJYRldnU0MxcDBJTWdSTkhoZThsTUtfeVBFd0o4YnRnVU12TkI4Zw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pa